{"tid":1059261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"愛吃炸雞懶得動　17歲高中生嘗禁果整個軟趴趴","createTime":"2019-03-13T04:24:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T06:35:02.000Z","uid":1735,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0e222e4246906401dae05ba28c7f9e71fb80d706","tid":1059261,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:24:05.000Z","msg":"1名高中生愛吃炸雞等速食又不愛運動，初戀想嘗禁果，竟發現自己「軟趴趴」，就醫才知膽固醇數值爆表，導致不到20歲就不舉。<br />\n今日出版的《自由時報》報導，1名17歲高中生嗜吃炸雞又不愛運動，身材爆肥，第一次交女友想要性行為，未料關鍵時刻卻「不舉」。就醫才知道膽固醇數值高達300mg/dL（正常為200mg/dL) ，因壞膽固醇過高沉積血管壁，造成陰莖海綿體充血不足，因此勃起有障礙。<br />\n<br />\n義大大昌醫院泌尿科醫師王起杰，協助他調整飲食、要求運動減重，再給降膽固醇藥物，也用低劑量威而鋼、犀利士等血管擴張劑，把血管撐開，性功能應可回復正常。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"ac5278f3a2daff301c12dfddf5397e2ef45497fe","tid":1059261,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:24:19.000Z","msg":"Link<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20190313/1532279/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20190313%2F1532279%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BT%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=2ce01f0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20190313%2F1532279%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=a2c6810c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20190313/1532279/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"fafdd2e8e06c259134566509c34c56a8d7434667","tid":1059261,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:24:38.000Z","msg":"不舉就不舉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/ha